{"tid":1638860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【低處未算低】林鄭民望再創新低 反對率達八成 評分 22.3 分","createTime":"2019-10-08T12:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:13:58.000Z","uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b3f1a41e6023db05f8c329f735a220e042e82b","tid":1638860,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:28:40.000Z","msg":"立場報道<br />\n【低處未算低】林鄭民望再創新低 反對率達八成 評分 22.3 分<br />\n2019/10/8 &mdash; 18:14<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥民望再創新低。香港民意研究所今發布主要官員最新民望數字，林鄭最新評分為 22.3 分，較上次調查再跌 2.6 分，為歷史新低；支持率淨值為負 65%，亦是史上最低紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n香港民研於 9 月 30 日至 10 月 3 日期間，訪問了 1004 人，顯示特首林鄭月娥的評分為 22.3 分，較上一次下跌 2.6 分，再創歷任特首新低，亦較自己 8 月份所創的最低紀錄（24.6 分）低。林鄭支持率跌至 15%，反對率升至 80%，淨支持率（支持率減反對率）為負 65%，同樣是上任以來及歷任特首新低。<br />\n<br />\n其他主要官員民望方面，律政司司長鄭若驊評分只得 14.7 分，較上次調查再跌 3 分；支持率淨值為負 68%，跌 10 個百分點，亦為歷史新低；教育局局長楊潤雄支持率淨值為負 50%，較上次調查跌 18 個百分點；保安局局長李家超支持率淨值為負 53%，跌 7 個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%8E%E8%99%95%E6%9C%AA%E7%AE%97%E4%BD%8E-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%8E%87%E9%81%94%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90-%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86-22-3-%E5%88%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25AE%2597%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%2586-22-3-%25E5%2588%2586%2F&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=fc170158\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BD%258E%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%25AE%2597%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2588%2586-22-3-%25E5%2588%2586%2F&h=64ee5b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BD%8E%E8%99%95%E6%9C%AA%E7%AE%97%E4%BD%8E-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%8E%87%E9%81%94%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90-%E8%A9%95%E5%88%86-22-3-%E5%88%86/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BTW,  請支持立場新聞 ,</span></strong><br />\n<strong>唔好貼咁多 紅媒01 , 明報 , 東方 </strong>"},{"pid":"d4add21ad27534bbc7d43b0a2135b79a1d0bd9eb","tid":1638860,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/clclccv-10_Hd0lK_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fclclccv-10_Hd0lK_1200x0.png&h=ab5dcdde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">痴撚線 ,  15% 支持度 仲覺得自己既政策得到廣泛市民支持</span></strong>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af60ee928b7eef1a9ee5d8e975ab3bb797b4055","tid":1638860,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:33:04.000Z","msg":"死閪婆 <br />\n<br />\n依個世界邊個地方夠香港癲 ?"},{"pid":"a0e48c2edaa8e84f663925c02de742b93fa547bb","tid":1638860,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"反對率  分分鐘仲勁過 啲戰亂獨裁國家 <br />\n<br />\n20% 劣幣藍屍人口都護唔撚住條閪婆"},{"pid":"c83a384772be18f5f6584978754a1eac8123f5e9","tid":1638860,"uid":47783,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:13:58.000Z","msg":"呢位ching轉風向都幾勁(2)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/857312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/857312</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知挫敗狗近牌重帶唔帶得郁風向呢？"}]}